Package: wordembeddings
Type: Package
Title: Create customized word embeddings using a grammar of model (hyper)parameters
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Louis", "Teitelbaum", email = "louist@post.bgu.ac.il", role = c("cre", "aut", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9347-0145"))
Description: The various algorithms for training word embeddings (e.g. word2vec, 
    GloVe, fastText, PPMI SVD) share common underlying principles, but these 
    principles are often obscured by the choices made in particular 
    implementations. 'wordembeddings' makes the assumptions underlying these 
    algorithms explicit with a comprehensive grammar of model parameters and 
    hyperparameters. The user can train embeddings using any of the traditional 
    frameworks, or mix and match elements to fit a particular application.
